## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the inherent uncertainties in climate modeling. While the sources used are reputable, the rapidly evolving nature of climate science means that new findings could alter current understandings. Additionally, the complexity of climate systems and their interactions with natural disasters means that predictions and assessments are subject to change as more data becomes available.

